## Animations (Keep Simple)
- Slide: Screen transitions
- Fade: Content changes
- Scale: Button press feedback
- Shake: Error feedback
- Pop: Success celebrations

## Feedback Messages
- Short and encouraging
- Immediate (not delayed)
- Visual + optional sound
- Clear what to do next

## Gamification
- Daily streaks
- XP points per task
- Achievements/badges
- Leaderboards (optional)
- Progress tracking

